text: Congrats, Hiwa!!!

Need help preparing for interviews? Worried about case interviews? Need to get to the next level? WE GOT YOU!

With a lot of people going into interviews I wanted to point out a great resource available to all. If you need any help with interviews, especially case interviews please use these mentors! The below is posted and pinned in the SCA chat for your convenience!

Case Mentors - they can do a 45-minute case, mini-case/strategy questions, resume review, and behavior interviews.  If you desire something other than a 45min case please let them know prior.
Please schedule time with these mentors. If the available times don't work please get in touch with the case mentor and they will try to accommodate your schedule.
List of Case Mentors, with calendars invites, and emails. (you can also slack them)

One last call for Chili Competition Sign-ups

*<http://signupgenius.com|signupgenius.com>*

Get ready to spice things up at our MBA Chili Competition! It's time to put your culinary skills to the test and show off your family's secret chili recipe.
Bring your A-game, your appetite, and your competitive spirit. Whether you're a chili connoisseur or a first-time cook, this event is for you. Prizes, bragging rights, and, of course, the coveted title of "MBA Chili Champion" are up for grabs.
Don't miss out on this sizzling opportunity to connect, compete, and enjoy some delicious chili!
Award categories will include: Best Overall, Most like Mom's, Best Smoked Chili, and Best Sweet & Spicy Chili.
